{"tid":1745530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈 警查來源動機","createTime":"2019-11-22T09:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:46:57.000Z","uid":207111,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2bceb7aa26c4286ada3371d771bbd567d6765e","tid":1745530,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈 警查來源動機<br />\n<br />\n現場是洗衣街239號旁邊一條橫巷，警方下午約3時接獲市民報案，指上址發現一批汽油彈。警員到場，將現場圍封調查。經點算後，初步證實有4盆汽油彈，每盆有10多枚，警方在場另檢獲多個空樽及仍未入樽的汽油。<br />\n<br />\n涉案現場對面是界限街1號體育館，周日將作為區議會選舉投票站，警方正追查該批汽油彈的來源及使用動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QGJo2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QGJo2o&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=19768983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QGJo2o</a><br />\n<br />\n#新聞"},{"pid":"34cc1ffaced94d74601751011b39c332a1ca840e","tid":1745530,"uid":81385,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"取消區選/警察監票劇本"},{"pid":"8a13afa4323955f69e184a8f495d25f45fe2ee4e","tid":1745530,"uid":68463,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"又做大龍鳳嚇人"},{"pid":"479bc7302c4ace6c61703d16a07460577f64f4a2","tid":1745530,"uid":125357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"來源未就係警慌囉"},{"pid":"e75f0efadcc2c332776ab5be9b485745dd47f6d3","tid":1745530,"uid":45672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"何妖：。屌。"},{"pid":"3261d0fd736c4b8b6902066b66f309a7c740ac7f","tid":1745530,"uid":266176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"黑警又開始做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bc1bd64063ff4317b65934d707f41769a961c5","tid":1745530,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"全港咁多投票站，有乜嘢地方係唔近投票站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066544f4db8cb2095e5e4ccb1c46f87c02626c69","tid":1745530,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"50支啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6658b55422d850abc75976ddc8c2502cfed5125","tid":1745530,"uid":189564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"聲稱係中大收收埋埋幾千個<br />\n原來得50個 仲要擺出黎擺都光明正大<br />\n方死唔知係你政府做"},{"pid":"1f11c869f836568f8734ab7b2ca317f17abde300","tid":1745530,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"永遠有d 咩大事之前，死差佬就會做埋d 小動作，69定612前得一支汽油彈夠膽死去扔警察總部狗車、831 前拉議員，十足d 極權國家做既野"},{"pid":"43c3034ef38816f966e0da4aebafbee342eaaae4","tid":1745530,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"係咪覺得好多人都知應該投邊個？唔好成日連登圍爐，同我forward曬比你身邊嘅人，入到嗰網簡返自己嗰區，就知要投邊個藍邊個黃<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=f3e355e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk</a>"},{"pid":"8e8f95bd77bcf2c1311e89420b2a0cb3aab974ff","tid":1745530,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=b9f136fc\